

# 🏊 SwimTrack Pro

SwimTrack Pro is a personal coaching management app built with Streamlit. It helps coaches manage swimmers, bookings, schedules, locations, and payments in a simple, real‑world workflow.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 👤 Guest & Admin login
- 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 Swimmer management
- 📅 Booking with smart validations (no past dates/times)
- 🔒 Edit/Delete lock after session (with grace period)
- 📍 Address capture (Google Maps link or full address)
- 💰 Payment tracking & reset
- 📊 Admin dashboard (grouped by owner)
- 🎨 Visual calendar with status (upcoming/completed)
- ☁️ Google Sheets as cloud database
- 📱 Clean, responsive UI

---

## 🧠 Key Business Logic

- Prevent booking in the past (date & time)
- Dynamic time slot filtering (only future slots shown for today)
- Ownership-based access (users edit only their own entries)
- Post-session lock (no edits/deletes after cutoff)
- Graceful handling of missing fields (backward compatible data)
- Address shown at card-level or swimmer-level based on data

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- Python
- Streamlit
- Pandas
- Google Sheets API (`gspread`, `google-auth`)

---

## 📦 Local Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/muni-qa-engineer/swimtrack-pro.git
cd swimtrack-pro
pip install -r requirements.txt
streamlit run app.py
```

---

## 🔐 Configuration (Secrets)

Create `.streamlit/secrets.toml`:

```toml
[gcp_service_account]
type = "service_account"
project_id = "your-project-id"
private_key_id = "xxx"
private_key = "-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\nXXX\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----\n"
client_email = "xxx@xxx.iam.gserviceaccount.com"
client_id = "xxx"
auth_uri = "https://accounts.google.com/o/oauth2/auth"
token_uri = "https://oauth2.googleapis.com/token"
auth_provider_x509_cert_url = "https://www.googleapis.com/oauth2/v1/certs"
client_x509_cert_url = "xxx"
```

> Ensure your Google Sheet is shared with the service account email.

---

## 🗂️ Google Sheets Structure

### `students`
| name |
|------|

### `bookings`
| id | student | created_by | days | start_date | end_date | package | time | fee | status | method | duration | address |

---

## 🌐 Live App

Deployed on Streamlit Cloud.

---

## ⚠️ Known Limitations

- Current `save_data()` clears and rewrites sheets (not ideal for high concurrency)
- Delete sync in Sheets can be improved (row-level delete)

---

